{"tid":213688,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iPhone都可以自己買料砌機！鬼佬示範齋買零件成功砌成iPhone","createTime":"2017-04-23T09:51:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-23T10:07:48.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a6f3584cf7c013f0f725402ef36218fecc27bee4","tid":213688,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T09:51:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>iPhone都可以自己買料砌機！鬼佬示範齋買零件成功砌成iPhone<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2017/04/15/iphone-handmake/mobile-phone/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2017%2F04%2F15%2Fiphone-handmake%2Fmobile-phone%2F&d=aFheyUS8Hi5o9a%2F4VMBAnWMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=cf3d354b\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2017/04/15/iphone-handmake/mobile-phone/</a></strong></div></span><br />\n<br />\n講到砌機，就當然想到去黃金砌部電腦，但有一位都老外就突發其想，在只允許購買零件的條件之下，從零開始，砌一部可正常運作的iPhone出來，後來他真的成功了。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/snap2802-768x508.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F04%2Fsnap2802-768x508.png&h=35b70eb7&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n這位老外的名字叫Scotty Allen，在YouTube分享了他玩iPhone砌機的影片。他從底殼開始入手，在深圳的市場上找到了一個回收的二手底殼，還附隨了按鈕。之後買入了表面的玻璃跟液晶顯示屏，但黏合顯示屏與玻璃需要專業的儀器，最後找到了一間維修店代工完成。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/snap2800-768x441.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F04%2Fsnap2800-768x441.png&h=1f760acd&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n最複雜的當然是iPhone的底板。雖然Scotty得到了一塊生產線找來的底板的線路板，但上面沒有處理器也沒有記憶體。阿Scotty就市場上購買每一粒晶片，但發現要將晶片錫銲到底板是極為困難，迫於無奈之下，在市場上買入現成的底板，即是從舊iPhone裡面拆出來的底板。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(他購入的是iPhone 6s主機板)</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/snap2801-768x532.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F04%2Fsnap2801-768x532.png&h=b4329a48&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n在購入了電池、背板、主板、屏幕後，還有大量零件需要購買，在市場上Scotty順利買齊了排線、Lightening接口、耳機接口，甚至相機模組，店家還送他一堆螺絲，可知大部份零件組合到iPhone都是用同一款螺絲。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/snap2804-768x471.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F04%2Fsnap2804-768x471.png&h=f2ca7a8f&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n幾經波折之下，花了無數小時的組裝，終於完成了一部可真正使用的iPhone。雖然在香港很多人已經知道大陸手機零件甚麼都有，但真正實行砌機並拍成短片的是Scotty Allen。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/snap2799-768x450.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F04%2Fsnap2799-768x450.png&h=8e15307b&s={SIZE}\" />[center]<br />\n<br />\n[center]砌iPhone片：<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=leFuF-zoVzA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DleFuF-zoVzA&d=aFheyUS8Hi5o9a%2F4VMBAnWMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=217afb03\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=leFuF-zoVzA</a></div>"},{"pid":"bf6b150eaa04341f81cf07a0c9ee536b4b7d5d9e","tid":213688,"uid":53736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T09:52:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6982873163fb6444153f15df0ba592e48a9b0f52","tid":213688,"uid":2403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T09:52:36.000Z","msg":"Wow"},{"pid":"bece19b4ca7ac3f25f3e92c574f4537c1e10c7cc","tid":213688,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T09:54:22.000Z","msg":"old news is so 唔識串"},{"pid":"6063dc99ce385354cc52a20ef0b435288427b7c7","tid":213688,"uid":97558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T09:55:01.000Z","msg":"Touch ID 跟主機板，姐係廢咗冇得用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feca51c1e12e4b7593a769628f9c6875f6b2981b","tid":213688,"uid":53736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T09:57:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Touch ID 跟主機板，姐係廢咗冇得用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁都有位入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ce0421845a0e496292dcdce9a7366f802f693d8","tid":213688,"uid":5137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T10:07:14.000Z","msg":"Wow"},{"pid":"94322328fa15cbef15e1596f2f891a7860adb84b","tid":213688,"uid":2107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T10:07:48.000Z","msg":"wow"}]}